en Erfahrungsschatz von Jahrtausenden in der Anwendung von nat\\u00fcrlichen Arzneimitteln und Therapien, gerade auch f\\u00fcr die Pr\\u00e4vention und Behandlung von Infektionskrankheiten.\\n\\nIm Bem\\u00fchen wirksame Medikamente gegen die Infektion und Erkrankung von Covid-19 zu finden, wurden inzwischen ... \\n\\nLesen Sie hier den ganzen Beitrag: \\nhttps:\\/\\/www.ayurveda.de\\/covid-19-warum-so-wenig-empfehlungen-zur-staerkung-des-immunsystems\\/", "language": null, "image": "https://scontent-muc2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/127242221_3357934317593277_1386848674000665530_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s480x480&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=7afa59&_nc_ohc=ZHS5KBL-3ukAX96swxv&_nc_ht=scontent-muc2-1.xx&oh=00_AfA7zClysziyJbLtUNZACE7pODVQnZmcY7gMSNOPN1R8WA&oe=6562BF06", "pagetype": "socialmediaposting", "links": ["https://www.facebook.com/", "https://www.facebook.com/recover/initiate?lwv=110&ars=royal_blue_bar", "/r.php?locale=de_DE", "/login/?privacy_mutation_token=eyJ0eXBlIjowLCJjcmVhdGlvbl90aW1lIjoxNjk4MzgyNzI3LCJjYWxsc2l0ZV9pZCI6Mzc4Mzc1MTU5OTY2NjIxfQ%3D%3D&next=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2F100063864408388", "/reg/?privacy_mutation_token=eyJ0eXBlIjowLCJjcmVhdGlvbl90aW1lIjoxNjk4MzgyNzI3LCJjYWxsc2l0ZV9pZCI6Mzc4Mzc1MTU5OTY2NjIxfQ%3D%3D&rs=2", "https://www.facebook.com/recover/initiate?lwv=110&ars=royal_blue_bar", "/reg/?privacy_mutation_token=eyJ0eXBlIjowLCJjcmVhdGlvbl90aW1lIjoxNjk4MzgyNzI3LCJjYWxsc2l0ZV9pZCI6NjQ4NzMxOTgyNDk1ODQyfQ%3D%3D&rs=1", "#", "https://facebook.com/thework.punkt.berlin?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/thework.punkt.berlin?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/MeditationBob?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/MeditationBob?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/YogaXperience?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/YogaXperience?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/volkerheppcoaching?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/volkerheppcoaching?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/ayurvedaportal?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/ayurvedaportal?ref=py_c", "https://facebook.com/purnamreisen?ref=py